<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TERRA 563 — Santa Teresita, Guadalajara</title>
<meta name="description" content="TERRA 563: desarrollo boutique de 9 departamentos en Santa Teresita, Guadalajara. Elevador, roof top con asador, acceso controlado.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#EAE4D6;
    --paper-2:#DED6C4;
    --ink:#17140F;
    --ink-soft:#4A463C;
    --concrete:#B9B2A5;
    --concrete-2:#8C8477;
    --brick:#9C4A2E;
    --brick-2:#7C3620;
    --steel:#33454C;
    --garden:#55684A;
    --gold:#C79A7D;
    --line:rgba(23,20,15,.16);
    --display:'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    --body:'Inter', sans-serif;
    --mono:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); font-family:var(--body);
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  a{color:inherit;}
  img,svg{display:block; max-width:100%;}
  .wrap{max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 32px;}
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.18em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--brick);
  }
  .rule{height:1px; background:var(--line);}

  /* ===== NAV ===== */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(234,228,214,.9); backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  nav{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:20px 0;
  }
  .logo{
    font-family:var(--display); font-weight:700; font-size:20px; letter-spacing:.06em;
  }
  .logo span{color:var(--brick);}
  .navlinks{display:flex; gap:34px; font-size:14px;}
  .navlinks a{text-decoration:none; opacity:.75; transition:opacity .2s;}
  .navlinks a:hover{opacity:1;}
  .navcta{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.06em;
    background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); padding:11px 18px;
    text-decoration:none; white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .navcta:hover{background:var(--brick);}
  .navtoggle{display:none;}

  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero{
    padding:76px 0 40px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr; gap:56px; align-items:center;
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-family:var(--display); font-weight:700;
    font-size:clamp(48px,6.6vw,84px); line-height:.96; letter-spacing:-.01em;
    margin-top:18px;
  }
  .hero h1 em{font-style:normal; color:var(--brick);}
  .hero p.lead{
    margin-top:22px; font-size:18px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--ink-soft); max-width:46ch;
  }
  .hero .loc{
    margin-top:16px; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.05em; color:var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .hero-ctas{display:flex; gap:14px; margin-top:34px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.04em;
    padding:15px 24px; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; border:1.5px solid var(--ink);
    transition:transform .15s ease, background .15s ease, color .15s ease;
  }
  .btn-solid{background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper);}
  .btn-solid:hover{background:var(--brick); border-color:var(--brick); transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .btn-outline{background:transparent; color:var(--ink);}
  .btn-outline:hover{background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); transform:translateY(-1px);}

  .hero-visual{position:relative;}
  .hero-visual svg{width:100%; height:auto;}

  .stat-strip{
    margin-top:64px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  }
  .stat{padding:26px 6px; text-align:left; border-left:1px solid var(--line);}
  .stat:first-child{border-left:none;}
  .stat .n{font-family:var(--display); font-weight:700; font-size:32px;}
  .stat .l{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.08em; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:6px; text-transform:uppercase;}

  /* ===== SECTION shells ===== */
  section{padding:96px 0;}
  .section-head{max-width:640px; margin-bottom:52px;}
  .section-head h2{
    font-family:var(--display); font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(30px,3.4vw,44px);
    margin-top:14px; letter-spacing:-.01em;
  }
  .section-head p{margin-top:16px; color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:16px; line-height:1.65;}

  /* ===== CONCEPTO ===== */
  .concept{background:var(--paper-2);}
  .materials{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:1px; background:var(--line);
    border:1px solid var(--line); margin-top:8px;
  }
  .material{background:var(--paper-2); padding:26px 22px;}
  .material .sw{width:26px; height:26px; margin-bottom:16px;}
  .material h3{font-family:var(--display); font-size:17px; font-weight:600;}
  .material p{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:8px; line-height:1.5;}

  /* ===== UNIDADES ===== */
  .floors{
    margin-top:8px; border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .floor-row{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:110px 1fr 160px 220px; align-items:center;
    padding:20px 24px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); gap:16px;
  }
  .floor-row:first-child{border-top:none;}
  .floor-row.head{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-soft);
    padding:14px 24px;
  }
  .floor-tag{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:14px; font-weight:500;}
  .floor-desc{font-size:15px;}
  .floor-desc b{font-weight:600;}
  .floor-area{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:14px;}
  .floor-tags{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:flex-end;}
  .pill{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:.04em;
    border:1px solid var(--line); padding:5px 9px; color:var(--ink-soft);
  }
  .pill.on{border-color:var(--brick); color:var(--brick);}

  .unit-note{
    margin-top:22px; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-soft); max-width:64ch; line-height:1.6;
  }

  /* ===== AMENIDADES ===== */
  .amen-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1px; background:var(--line);
    border:1px solid var(--line); margin-top:8px;
  }
  .amen{background:var(--paper); padding:34px 28px; min-height:180px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:space-between;}
  .amen .idx{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; color:var(--brick);}
  .amen h3{font-family:var(--display); font-size:19px; font-weight:600; margin-top:26px;}
  .amen p{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:8px; line-height:1.5;}

  /* ===== ACABADOS ===== */
  .finishes{margin-top:8px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:28px 48px;}
  .finish-item{display:flex; gap:16px; align-items:flex-start;}
  .finish-item .dot{width:7px; height:7px; background:var(--brick); margin-top:9px; flex:none;}
  .finish-item b{font-family:var(--display); font-size:16px; font-weight:600; display:block;}
  .finish-item span{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.5;}

  /* ===== UBICACION ===== */
  .location{background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper);}
  .location .eyebrow{color:var(--gold);}
  .location .section-head p{color:#B9B2A5;}
  .loc-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:56px; align-items:start;}
  .loc-list{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:22px;}
  .loc-list li{list-style:none; padding-left:22px; position:relative; font-size:15px; color:#DDD6C6; line-height:1.55;}
  .loc-list li:before{content:"→"; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--brick);}
  .loc-list b{color:var(--paper); font-family:var(--display); font-weight:600;}
  .map-frame{
    border:1px solid #4A463C; aspect-ratio:1/1; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
    background:
      linear-gradient(#26241D 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0/40px 40px,
      linear-gradient(90deg,#26241D 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0/40px 40px,
      #1E1B15;
  }
  .map-pin{
    position:absolute; left:52%; top:46%; width:16px; height:16px; background:var(--brick);
    border:3px solid var(--paper); border-radius:50%;
  }
  .map-frame .addr{
    position:absolute; left:20px; bottom:20px; right:20px;
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; color:#B9B2A5; line-height:1.6;
  }

  /* ===== PRECIO ===== */
  .price-wrap{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr; gap:56px; align-items:start;}
  .price-card{
    border:1px solid var(--line); padding:40px;
  }
  .price-card .from{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.08em; color:var(--ink-soft); text-transform:uppercase;}
  .price-card .val{font-family:var(--display); font-weight:700; font-size:56px; margin-top:10px;}
  .price-card .val span{color:var(--brick);}
  .price-card .ticket{margin-top:18px; font-size:15px; color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .price-list{margin-top:30px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0;}
  .price-list div{
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:14px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line); font-size:14px;
  }
  .price-list div span:first-child{color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .price-list div span:last-child{font-family:var(--mono);}

  .scheme h3{font-family:var(--display); font-size:19px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:18px;}
  .scheme-bar{display:flex; height:14px; border:1px solid var(--ink); overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:14px;}
  .scheme-bar div:nth-child(1){width:30%; background:var(--brick);}
  .scheme-bar div:nth-child(2){width:50%; background:var(--concrete-2);}
  .scheme-bar div:nth-child(3){width:20%; background:var(--garden);}
  .scheme-legend{display:flex; gap:22px; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .scheme-legend span{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px;}
  .scheme-legend i{width:9px; height:9px; display:inline-block;}
  .scheme-note{margin-top:20px; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.6;}

  /* ===== CONTACTO ===== */
  .contact{background:var(--paper-2);}
  .contact-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr; gap:64px;}
  .contact-info p{margin-top:16px; font-size:15px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.6; max-width:42ch;}
  .contact-details{margin-top:34px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;}
  .contact-details div{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:14px;}
  .contact-details div b{display:block; font-family:var(--body); font-weight:600; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom:4px;}

  form{display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;}
  .form-row{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px;}
  input, select, textarea{
    width:100%; font-family:var(--body); font-size:14px; padding:14px 16px;
    border:1px solid var(--ink); background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink);
  }
  textarea{resize:vertical; min-height:90px;}
  label{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom:6px; display:block;}
  .form-submit{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:.04em;
    background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); border:none; padding:16px 24px; cursor:pointer;
    margin-top:6px;
  }
  .form-submit:hover{background:var(--brick);}
  .form-hint{font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-top:2px;}

  footer{padding:38px 0; border-top:1px solid var(--line);}
  .foot-row{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px;}
  .foot-row .logo{font-size:16px;}
  .foot-meta{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-soft); letter-spacing:.04em;}

  @media(max-width:920px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .hero-visual{order:-1;}
    .stat-strip{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .stat:nth-child(3){border-left:none;}
    .materials{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .amen-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .floor-row{grid-template-columns:80px 1fr; row-gap:8px;}
    .floor-area,.floor-tags{grid-column:2; justify-content:flex-start;}
    .finishes{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .loc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .price-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .navlinks{display:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="wrap">
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">TERRA<span> 563</span></div>
      <div class="navlinks">
        <a href="#concepto">Concepto</a>
        <a href="#unidades">Unidades</a>
        <a href="#amenidades">Amenidades</a>
        <a href="#ubicacion">Ubicación</a>
        <a href="#precio">Precio</a>
      </div>
      <a href="#contacto" class="navcta">AGENDAR VISITA →</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Preventa · Santa Teresita, Guadalajara</div>
        <h1>Vivir en<br><em>escala boutique</em></h1>
        <p class="lead">9 departamentos de 35 m² en un edificio de diseño distintivo, a pasos de Chapultepec y Av. México. Concreto aparente, ladrillo y herrería expuesta — arquitectura pensada para quien valora su espacio, no la masividad.</p>
        <div class="loc">MANUEL M. DIÉGUEZ 563 · SANTA TERESITA · 44600 GUADALAJARA, JAL.</div>
